Interface GeneralReposInterface

All Superinterfaces:
Remote
All Known Implementing Classes:
GeneralRepos
public interface GeneralReposInterface extends Remote
Operational interface of a remote object of type GeneralRepository. It provides the functionality to access the GeneralRepository.
